- `{{.Path}}/**` -> 读取 `{{.Path}}/.agents/skills/{{.SkillName}}/SKILL.md` 或 `{{.Path}}/.claude/skills/{{.SkillName}}/SKILL.md`，并按需读取 `{{.Path}}/.agents/skills/{{.SkillName}}/references/project-spec.md`
